    </p>

    <p>
        <strong>Q: What's the point of the coins?</strong>
        <br>
        <strong>A:</strong> Their only purpose is to be used in the prize machine to unlock new characters. They do not affect your score or gameplay abilities.
    </p>

    <p>
        <strong>Q: Why did an eagle take me away?</strong>
        <br>
        <strong>A:</strong> This happens when you stay in one place for too long or move too many steps backward. The game is designed to keep you moving forward.
